                  "revisionId": 2676559,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "If the remaining sleep duration of a re-triggered field is short enough, and the field duration long enough, enemies can be 'chain slept', falling asleep and waking up repeatedly until the field expires."
                }
